description: Premier South Boston developers have done it again! Beautiful Boutique building in the center of South Boston! Be the 1st to live in this stunning duplex with parking! Entertainers dream layout spanning over 2300 SF! Towering ceilings & natural light flood the home! Sleek chef's kitchen w/ designer Thermador appliance package w/ integrated refrigerator, 2 drawer dishwasher, sparkling 2 tone cabinets, floor + cabinet level lighting and waterfall quartz island. Kitchen opens to a well-proportioned dining + living area with a fireplace. Impressive primary bedroom w/ walk-in closet & spa quality bath + a sizable 2nd bedroom + 2nd full bath on the first level. Downstairs boasts an enormous family/media room ready to be finished into a dream entertainment area! There is also a 3rd bedroom as well, beautifully appointed 3rd bath + XL bonus room perfect for a home gym or studio. Laundry, C/A, modern lighting + fixtures throughout + parking! Impeccable attention to detail + flawless floorplan!
